      <dependency task="012" status="required">
        D2-03 — `SessionSummarizeOrchestrator` concrete class. The tool DELEGATES to this
        orchestrator's shared internal Summarize method; does not re-implement Summarize
        logic. Task 012 MUST be ✅ before task 015 begins.
      </dependency>
      <dependency task="005" status="required-implicitly">
        D1-05 — `FieldDelta` SSE event variant on `AnalysisChunk`. The orchestrator emits
        these progressive events; this tool inherits emission via delegation.
      </dependency>
      <dependency task="006" status="required-implicitly">
        D1-06 — Azure OpenAI Structured Outputs + incremental JSON parser. Underpins the
        orchestrator's streaming output; this tool inherits via delegation.
      </dependency>
    </dependencies>
    <related-work>
      <item>Task 014 (D2-04) — direct endpoint `POST /api/ai/chat/sessions/{id}/summarize`.
        Parallel-safe sibling in P2-G3. Both task 014 and task 015 converge on the SAME
