      <item>Task 020 (D2-11) — chat-pane orchestration UX (file chips, indicator,
        multi-file combined-summary interjection). Front-end counterpart that
        UI-renders the streaming `FieldDelta` events emitted when this tool is invoked.</item>
      <item>R2 task 060 / 061 — Direct OpenAI agent + agent-factory extension that
        established the `SprkChatAgentFactory` middleware stack pattern referenced
        throughout this task.</item>
      <item>R2 task 063 — Per-tool error isolation (AIPU2-063). The tool's
        registration block follows the same `try/catch + failedTools.Add(...)` pattern.</item>
    </related-work>
  </context>

  <steps>
    <step order="0" name="Context Check + RIGOR LEVEL declaration">
      Check context usage. If &gt; 70%, run `context-handoff` and request `/compact`.
